\c 10
\s Rudzi rwaAhabhi navaporofita vaBhaari vanoparadzwa
\p
\v 1 Zvino Ahabhi waiva ane vanakomana vana makumi manomwe paSamaria. Jehu ndokunyora tsamba, ndokudzitumira kuSamaria kumisoro yeJezereeri, vakuru, nekuvareri vevana vaAhabhi, achiti:
\v 2 Zvino ikozvino pakusvika kwetsamba iyi kwamuri, vanakomana vatenzi wangu zvavari kwamuri, uye ngoro nemabhiza zviri kwamuri, neguta rakashoshewa, nezvombo;
\v 3 zvionerei wakanakisisa uye wakafanira kuvanakomana vatenzi wenyu, muise pachigaro cheushe chababa vake, uye murwire imba yatenzi wenyu.
\v 4 Asi vakatya zvikuru, ndokuti: Tarirai, madzimambo maviri haana kumira pamberi pake, zvino isu tichamira sei?
\v 5 Zvino mutariri weimba nemutariri weguta, nevakuru, nevareri vevana vakatuma kuna Jehu, vachiti: Tiri varanda venyu, uye zvese zvamuchareva kwatiri tichaita. Hatingaisi munhu ave mambo. Itai zvakanaka pameso enyu.
\p
\v 6 Zvino wakavanyorera tsamba rwechipiri achiti: Kana muri vangu uye muchiteerera kuinzwi rangu, torai misoro yevarume ava, vanakomana vamambo wenyu, mugouya kwandiri kuJezereeri mangwana nenguva inenge ino. Zvino vanakomana vamambo, vanhu makumi manomwe, vaiva kuvakuru veguta vaivarera.
\v 7 Zvino zvakaitika pakusvika kwetsamba kwavari, kuti vakatora vanakomana vamambo, ndokuuraya vanhu makumi manomwe, ndokuisa misoro yavo mumatengu, ndokutumira kwaari kuJezereeri.
\p
\v 8 Zvino kwakauya nhume ndokumuudza ichiti: Vaunza misoro yevanakomana vamambo. Iye ndokuti: Iitei mirwi miviri pamukova wesuwo kusvika mangwanani.
\v 9 Zvino zvakaitika mangwanani, kuti wakabuda ndokumira ndokuti kuvanhu vese: Imwi makarurama, ini ndakarongera tenzi wangu, ndokumuuraya, asi ndiani wauraya ava vese?
\v 10 Zivai ikozvino kuti hakungawiri chinhu pasi pashoko raJehovha, Jehovha raakataura pamusoro peimba yaAhabhi; nokuti Jehovha wakaita zvaakataura neruoko rwemuranda wake Eria.
\v 11 Naizvozvo Jehu wakauraya vese vaiva vasara veimba yaAhabhi muJezereeri, nevakuru vake vese, nevaifambidzana naye, nevapristi vake, kusvika asina kumusiira musiiwa.
\p
\v 12 Zvino wakasimuka ndokubva ndokuenda kuSamaria; paimba yekuveurira \add makwai\add* yevafudzi panzira,
\v 13 Jehu wakasangana nevanin'ina vaAhazi mambo waJudha, ndokuti: Ndimwi vana ani? Ivo ndokuti: Tiri vanin'ina vaAhazia, uye tinoburuka kutoburuka kundokwazisa vana vamambo navana vavahosi.
\v 14 Iye akati: Vabatei vari vapenyu. Vakavabata vari vapenyu, vakavauraya padziva reimba pavaiveura makwai, varume vaiva vana makumi mana navaviri; haana kusiya umwe wavo.
\p
\v 15 Zvino wakati abvapo, akasangana naJehonadhabhi mwanakomana waRekabhu, wanga achiuya kuzosangana naye; akamukwazisa, akati kwaari: Moyo wako wakarurama here, sokururama komoyo wangu kwauri? Jehonadhabhi akapindura, akati: Wakarurama hawo. Kana zvakadaro, ndibate ruoko rwangu. Iye akabata ruoko rwake, ndokumukwidza mungoro maakange ari.
\v 16 Akati: Hendei, undoona kushingaira kwandinoshingairira Jehovha nako. Naizvozvo vakamufambisa mungoro yake.
\v 17 Wakati asvika Samaria, akauraya vese vakange vasara vaAhabhi muSamaria, kusvikira amuparadza, neshoko raJehovha rakange rarehwa naEria.
\p
\v 18 Ipapo Jehu akaunganidza vanhu vese, akati kwavari: Ahabhi wakashumira Bhaari zvishoma, asi Jehu uchamushumira kwazvo.
\v 19 Naizvozvo zvino chidanai vaporofita vese vaBhaari, navese vanonamata kwaari, navapristi vake vese, vauye kwandiri; ngakurege kushaikwa kunyange nomumwe; nokuti ndinoda kubaira Bhaari chibairo chikuru; ani nani unoshaikwa haangararami. Asi Jehu wakaita izvozvo namano, achida kuuraya vanamati vaBhaari.
\v 20 Zvino Jehu akati: Tsaurirai Bhaari zuva romutambo mukuru. Vakaparidza izvozvo.
\v 21 Zvino Jehu akatuma nhume pakati paIsraeri pese, vese vanamati vaBhaari vakauya; hakuna munhu wakasara, akasauya. Vakapinda mumba maBhaari, imba yaBhaari ikazara, kusvika kumadziro nokumadziro.
\v 22 Akati kumutariri wenguvo: Vigira vanamati vaBhaari vese nguvo. Iye akavavigira nguvo.
\v 23 Ipapo Jehu akapinda mumba maBhaari, anaJehonadhabhi mwanakomana waRekabhi, akati kuvanamati vaBhaari: Tsvakai, mutarire kwazvo kuti pano pakati penyu parege kuva nomuranda umwe waJehovha, asi vanamati vaBhaari chete.
\v 24 Vakapinda kundobaira zvibairo nezvipiriso zvinopiswa. Zvino Jehu wakange araira varume vana makumi masere panze, achiti: Kana umwe wavarume vandinoisa pamaoko enyu akapukunyuka, munhu unomurega akapukunyuka, uchamufira.
\v 25 Zvino wakati apedza kubaira chipo chinopiswa Jehu akati kuvarindi nokuvakuru: Pindai, muvauraye; musatendera umwe kubuda. Ivo vakavauraya neminondo inopinza; varindi navakuru vakavarasira kunze, vakaenda kuguta reimba yaBhaari.
\v 26 Ipapo vakabudisa mbiru dzaiva mumba maBhaari, vakadzipisa.
\v 27 Vakaputsawo mbiru yaBhaari, vakaputsawo imba yaBhaari, vakaiita imba yembudzi kusvikira nhasi.
\v 28 Naizvozvo Jehu wakaparadza Bhaari pakati paIsraeri.
\p
\v 29 Asi Jehu haana kurega kutevera zvivi zvaJerobhoamu mwanakomana waNebhati, zvaakatadzisa Israeri nazvo, zvemhuru dzegoridhe dzaiva paBheteri, nedzaiva paDhani.
\v 30 Zvino Jehovha akati kuna Jehu: Zvawakaita zvakanaka ukaita zvakarurama pamberi pangu, ukaitira imba yaAhabhi zvese zvakange zviri mumoyo mangu, zvino vana vako vorudzi rwechina vachagara pachigaro choushe hwaIsraeri.
\v 31 Asi Jehu haana kurangarira kufamba nomoyo wese nomurairo waJehovha Mwari waIsraeri; haana kurega zvivi zvaJerobhoamu zvaakatadzisa Israeri nazvo.
\p
\v 32 Pamazuva iwayo Jehovha wakatanga kutapudza Israeri; Hazaeri akavakunda pamiganhu yese yaIsraeri,
\v 33 kubva kuna Joridhani zvichienda mabvazuva, nenyika yese yaGiriyadhi, neyavaGadhi, neyavaRubheni, neyavaManase, kubva paAroeri pamupata weArinoni, ndiro Giriyadhi neBhashani.
\p
\v 34 Zvino mamwe mabasa aJehu, nezvese zvaakaita, nesimba rake rese, hazvina kunyorwa here mubhuku yaMakoronike amadzimambo aIsraeri?
\v 35 Jehu akarara namadzibaba ake, vakamuviga paSamaria, Jehoahazi mwanakomana wake akamutevera paushe.
\v 36 Nguva yakabata Jehu ushe hwaIsraeri paSamaria aiva makore ana makumi maviri namasere.
